ce with GuestVoice K scores exceeding benchmarks, and achieving 98% in Marriott’s accounting rating system. \n\nSpearheaded the opening of Kissuisen, the hotel’s signature Japanese restaurant in collaboration with Michelin-starred Chef Matayoshi — now proudly listed in the 𝐌𝐈𝐂𝐇𝐄𝐋𝐈𝐍 𝐆𝐮𝐢𝐝𝐞 𝐓𝐡𝐚𝐢𝐥𝐚𝐧𝐝 — contributing to a projected 25% uplift in F&B revenue.", "experiences/1/jobEndedOn": "5-2025", "experiences/1/jobLocation": "Bangkok, Bangkok City, Thailand", "experiences/1/jobLocationCountry": "TH", "experiences/1/jobStartedOn": "12-2022", "experiences/1/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/1/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4E0BAQG5aEgM3ddEBg/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1631316200575?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=wFPRbDb203X4riTBPN2Snl4gVqukDxTm-owWs3NCnGQ", "experiences/1/title": "Executive Assistant Manager", "experiences/2/companyId": "214203", "experiences/2/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/2/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/the-ritz-carlton-hotel-company-llc/", "experiences/2/companyName": "The Ritz-Carlton Hotel Company, L.L.C.", "experiences/2/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/2/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:214203", "experiences/2/companyWebsite": "http://www.ritzcarlton.com/", "experiences/2/employmentType": "Full-time", "experiences/2/jobDescription": "•\tOversaw hotel operations in the absence of the General Manager, ensuring service excellence across all departments.\n•\tLed the GuestVoice program and championed brand standard audits within The Ritz-Carlton’s Quality department.\n•\tContributed to major sustainability efforts, including the implementation of a brand-new Eco Discovery Center.\n•\tCertified The Ritz-Carlton trainer, providing countdown opening support to other The Ritz-Carlton hotels.\n•\tOptimizing revenue and GOP of four specialty restaurants and bars during a major renovation.", "experiences/2/jobEndedOn": "1-2023", "experiences/2/jobLocation": "Langkawi", "experiences/2/jobLocati