ill succeed in his next role.\n\nWe wish Nisham continued success and growth. His leadership, professionalism, and dedication set a high standard—he will be missed, and we look forward to the possibility of working together again in the future.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Rif-ath Fareed", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Director of Human Resources at Alila Hotels", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/rif-ath-fareed-17085044/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAlhNeQBrYXEpZkh-7c-rgIxn7fsdELozOA", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Javokhir worked with Ali on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "July 26, 2022", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "Ali is person with full of energy and passion. Always helpful and flexible.", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Javokhir Boboev", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Beverage Manager Naama Beach Villas & Spa", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/javokhir-boboev-51a577160/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACaG5SYBEzVHYrUY5lRAKjoDzSK_ipUIPa4", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Dante managed Ali directly", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "May 27, 2021", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "Besides being a great bartender and colleague, Ned is a great all around individual. Takes responsibility and treats all the guests as if they are entering his home.\n\nExpert behind the bar, great knowledge on spirits and a guest favorite for his personality that brightens the room. \n", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Dante Rossi", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Director of Food & Beverage | Building High-Performance Teams", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/dante-rossi-luxury-hospitality/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABvGKIMBTv1moKi0wFzKliVDYOO3604wFHo", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Abdulla managed Ali directl